metadata.name: A bigger world.
metadata.description:
We live on this earth, we consume its resources, and grow old thinking that this planet is big, a never ending trip to many, and nothing more..

Little that we know, is that there is an endless world above us, a galaxy that is yet to be discovered..

We are simply a grain that’s part of a bigger universe, so I present to you in my hand: Our beautiful galaxy, an eternal existence that’s yet to be solved, just like the journey within yourself.. 

Start your journey, explore the world..
